{"tid":1062332,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐冠盃8強抽籤結果:巴塞vs曼城","createTime":"2019-03-15T04:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T12:16:10.000Z","uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8a2a7a51f7c900e9034276237f8f803ab8d01b51","tid":1062332,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:39:51.000Z","msg":"據英國《太陽報》報導，一份疑似歐冠盃8強抽籤結果在網絡媒體上泄露。有陰謀論者稱，這是歐洲足協總監意外泄露的，但很快就被其刪除了。<br />\n<br />\n根據網傳的圖片顯示，歐冠盃8強抽籤的結果為：利物浦vs阿積士，祖雲達斯vs波圖，曼聯vs熱刺，巴塞vs曼城。<br />\n<br />\n這一次《太陽報》很冷靜地分析道：這張圖片很有可能是徹頭徹尾的惡作劇，也可能是受關注度高的某Twitter用戶捏造的。<br />\n<br />\n歐冠盃8強將在香港時間今天晚上19:00進行，這張圖片的內容到底是真是假，很快就會真相大白。"},{"pid":"f6533873bebebcece2a67d3c64349a2316621c62","tid":1062332,"uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zWmuLBp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzWmuLBp.jpg&h=f8252247&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6eb503ab60918d5bbf5154bf30caa273d7c7a814","tid":1062332,"uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"老婦對波圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e5da98c063b2a42522dffc696e14e2b1978fe7","tid":1062332,"uid":92278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:41:59.000Z","msg":"屌 假撚到"},{"pid":"351247a4673cc21146e704db9ad3cb55f1a4f686","tid":1062332,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"上年唔係有流出咩？"},{"pid":"73635ab16dd406ba4567d83d8b05d06a3365e6ef","tid":1062332,"uid":131369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:43:55.000Z","msg":"燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ec8f0c2302db2236744850521d76a5d9a9376a","tid":1062332,"uid":153341,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:44:3